version_description: Basic chord structure arranged for guitar.
There are no other correct versions of this particular version of the song. This is the version from "this left feels right" and is correct.
Electric guitar using Barre chords distortion,chorus and compression effects,or if using acoustic simple open chords.
This version is a alternate way of playing the song compared to Version 1 and version 2. Standard Tuning and No Capo.
Perfect version for acoustic guitar. Using the proposed chords the execution will be similar to the original studio version, youtube link: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=beWIb9ZWHeY.
